title: launcher opens but nothing happens
body: i couldnt open league at all so i deleted it then redownloaded it. now the lol lancher opens but now the launcher literally does nothing. help pls

replies.body:
Hey Ryegor!

I can only imagine how frustrating it is to finally have the launcher open normally, only for it to not download the latest updates/patches >.<  Fortunately, we should be able to get this resolved!  There are a wide variety of different root causes as to why the patcher will not...ermm, well patch.  The following guide has the most common solutions to getting your launcher fully patched up:

https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues

If you are still staring at 0% and slowly tapping your fingers on your desk, don't give up all hope just yet!  Make sure to [submit a new ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) to our Tech Team so we can look into this issue further and provide further help!  If you do submit a ticket, include the following information:

1) Network Analysis: https://support.leagueoflegends.com/entries/27495980-Network-System-and-League-of-Legends-Logs#wq1

2) NetworkInfo Log: https://support.leagueoflegends.com/entries/27495980-Network-System-and-League-of-Legends-Logs#wq4

3) Process List: https://support.leagueoflegends.com/entries/27495980-Network-System-and-League-of-Legends-Logs#wq3
